WEBVTT

00:15:29.229 --> 00:15:31.631
i kroz period istraživanja od 200 dana,

00:15:31.631 --> 00:15:33.105
proučavali smo ples.

00:15:33.105 --> 00:15:37.001
Doveli smo plesače sa biološkim udovima

00:15:37.001 --> 00:15:39.666
i proučavali smo kako se kreću,

00:15:39.666 --> 00:15:43.166
koje sile primenjuju na plesnom podijumu

00:15:43.166 --> 00:15:44.717
i uzeli smo te podatke

00:15:44.717 --> 00:15:48.516
i uložili osnovne principe plesa,

00:15:48.516 --> 00:15:50.327
mogućnost refleksivnog plesa,

00:15:50.327 --> 00:15:51.852
i ugradili smo to znanje

00:15:51.852 --> 00:15:53.674
u bionički ud.

00:15:53.674 --> 00:15:55.950
U bionici se ne radi samo o tome da ljudi

00:15:55.950 --> 00:15:57.411
postanu jači i brži.

00:15:57.411 --> 00:15:59.753
Naš izraz, naša ljudskost,

00:15:59.753 --> 00:16:02.956
mogu se izraziti u elektromehanici.